                            <option>Basic (Clone, commit, push)</option>
                            <option>Intermediate (Branching, merging, PRs)</option>
                            <option>Comfortable (Resolve conflicts, rebase)</option>
                            <option>Advanced (Git workflows, best practices)</option>
                            <option>Expert (Complex operations, Git internals)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-field">
                        <label>6. Database comfort level?</label>
                        <select name="q6">
                            <option value="">Choose your level...</option>
                            <option>None (No database knowledge)</option>
                            <option>Basic (SELECT, INSERT queries)</option>
                            <option>Intermediate  (JOINS, subqueries)</option>
                            <option>Advanced  (Optimization, indexing)</option>
                            <option>SQL + NoSQL (MongoDB, Redis)</option>
                            <option>Multi-DB Expert (PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB)</option>
                            <option>Database Architect (Design, scaling)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-field">
                        <label>7. Math skills rating?</label>
                        <select name="q7">
                            <option value="">Choose your level...</option>
                            <option>Poor (Struggle with basic math)</option>
                            <option>Below Average (Can do basics only)</option>
                            <option>Average (Standard arithmetic, algebra)</option>
                            <option>Good (Calculus, statistics comfortable)</option>
                            <option>Very Good (Linear algebra, probability)</option>
                            <option>Excellent (Advanced math, research level)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-field">
                        <label>8. Machine Learning experience?</label>
                        <select name="q8">
                            <option value="">Choose your level...</option>
                            <option>No Experience (Never touched ML)</option>
                            <option>Beginner (Know concepts, no projects)</option>
                            <option>Basic (Built simple models with tutorials)</option>
                            <option>Intermediate (Can train models independently)</option>
